---
import {
  Accordion,
  AccordionContent,
  AccordionTrigger,
  AccordionItem,
} from "@/components/ui/accordion/";
---

<section id="faq" class="section">
  <sparkly-text
    number-of-sparkles="5"
    style="--sparkly-text-color: color-mix(in srgb, currentColor, var(--primary) 100%);"
  >
    <mark>these look fur-miliar</mark>
  </sparkly-text>

  <h2>FAQs</h2>
  <p>
    If you can’t find an answer to one of your burning questions, please get in
    touch. Hopefully though, we already have the answers right here!
  </p>
  <Accordion defaultValue="services">
    <AccordionItem value="services">
      <AccordionTrigger>What services do you offer?</AccordionTrigger>
      <AccordionContent>
        We offer bespoke web design, front-end web development and SEO. We build
        websites using the latest technologies and ensure they are responsive,
        accessible, and optimised for search engines.
      </AccordionContent>
    </AccordionItem>
    <AccordionItem value="why-us">
      <AccordionTrigger>Why should we choose you?</AccordionTrigger>
      <AccordionContent>
        We're certainly glad you're considering us! Our focus is on building
        accessible, responsive, and user-friendly websites. We pride ourselves
        on our attention to detail and our commitment to delivering high-quality
        work.
      </AccordionContent>
    </AccordionItem>
    <AccordionItem value="contact">
      <AccordionTrigger>How can I contact you?</AccordionTrigger>
      <AccordionContent>
        The best way to contact us is to fill out our form on our contact page.
        You can also email us directly at hello@kittycodecreative.com with any
        enquiries.
      </AccordionContent>
    </AccordionItem>
    <AccordionItem value="hosting">
      <AccordionTrigger>Is hosting included in your packages?</AccordionTrigger>
      <AccordionContent>
        Yes, all of our monthly packages include hosting charges. This enables
        us to keep your website up and running. If you stop your monthly
        payments before your contract expires, your hosting will also stop. If
        you're not on a monthly package, we can host for you for an additional
        fee.
      </AccordionContent>
    </AccordionItem>
    <AccordionItem value="seo">
      <AccordionTrigger>Do you offer SEO?</AccordionTrigger>
      <AccordionContent>
        Yes, all of our web packages include SEO as standard. While we can't
        guarantee a top spot on Google, we follow best practices to get your
        website ranking as well as possible and keep it discoverable across
        search engines and AI assistants.
      </AccordionContent>
    </AccordionItem>
    <AccordionItem value="maintenance">
      <AccordionTrigger
        >I already have a website, can you manage and update it for me?</AccordionTrigger
      >
      <AccordionContent>
        Absolutely! We have no set pricing for this sort of request, so it will
        depend on a case-by-case basis. Send us a message and we will gladly
        manage your website for you.
      </AccordionContent>
    </AccordionItem>
  </Accordion>
</section>
